{"type": "article", "id": 18864, "title": "和纸灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-11T08:52:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153141zvcJdPM4FZ6RE5YS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏白色的灯来自日本设计工作室 24d- Studio，采用传统和纸制作，并做了抗高温的处理。他们通过手工压制出了立体的折痕，然后将六边形或者五边形的图案拼在一起，上面有细腻的纹路。整体看上去很轻盈柔软，很唯美，有点像盖里设计的“云”。售价 130 美元，<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/japanese-rice-paper-airy-lamp-24d-studio/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153139YSjZm8JNcg0MGLEo.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615313902FNwsh4MlUojrtD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061531403rYXAEJvn1uHqaMK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061531408bxV1HMhBdN3lyiX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}